236
00:17:39,022 --> 00:17:43,023
- Myung Suk oppa tidak pulang semalam.
- Dia pergi kemana?

237
00:17:43,023 --> 00:17:44,074
Aku melihatnya saat pulang bekerja.

238
00:17:44,074 --> 00:17:48,006
- Dia menemui In Young.
- Apa?

239
00:17:48,006 --> 00:17:49,091
Dia menemui In Young?

240
00:17:49,091 --> 00:17:52,061
