245
00:18:12,062 --> 00:18:16,064
Apa-apaan ini?
Apa dia sudah gila?

246
00:18:16,064 --> 00:18:19,004
Kenapa dia memberi tahu hyungnim
kalau In Young disini?

247
00:18:29,023 --> 00:18:31,079
Hyungnim! Oh In Young!

248
00:18:33,015 --> 00:18:34,074
Adik ipar!

249
00:18:38,035 --> 00:18:40,035
Kenapa kau ada disini?

250
00:18:40,035 --> 00:18:42,064
Kenapa ahjussi ada disini?

251
00:19:12,069 --> 00:19:14,099
Kita bicarakan nanti.
